  <custodhist id="aspace_cc6658916b9cbb2d4cf1a12368aba9f2">
    <head>Custodial History</head>
<p>The materials making up this collection were donated by various former members of Stewardesses for Women's Rights after an SFWR reunion was held at the Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives, NYU, in the summer of 1987. The reunion was organized and the collection assembled by Wagner archivist Brenda Parnes. The majority of the records were donated by former SFWR National Coordinator, Nan Frost Weimers.</p>  </custodhist>
